snippet.title: Amber Heard Gaslighting Johnny Depp For An Hour (Uncensored Audio)
snippet.description:
These recordings were hard to find in their uncensored format without commentary and external opinions. I left out other recordings where family members and children were mentioned at length because I have a soul. I tried to think of a decent title for this video, but this is really just Amber Heard intimidating and gaslighting Johnny Depp for damn near an hour.

#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp #Metoo #Aquaman
